trainers.name: Hiker Gus
trainers.dialogue: I love the damp cave air!

trainers.name: Black Belt Justin
trainers.dialogue: This is my favourite training spot. Want to battle?

trainers.name: Black Belt Chad
trainers.dialogue: I have trained in this cave for years. I can't lose here!

trainers.name: Ace Trainer Michael
trainers.dialogue: I will test the sand team I am building against you.

trainers.name: Ace Trainer Jean
trainers.dialogue: Rumours say a rare fish resides in these cave waters.
